  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\nWhen editing the hyperlink in status chat input after moving the cursor using the mouse will delete the hyperlink. It works fine when editing after the cursor has been moved using left/right keys.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/47811206/e132200c-737e-4757-8202-fa81ac7c848d\r\n\r\n<!-- Provide a short description describing the problem you are experiencing. -->\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Insert an URL in statusChatInput\r\n2. Move the cursor inside the url\r\n3. Edit the URL\r\n<!-- example: step 1. do X step 2. do Y etc.. -->\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe URL is edited\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe URL is deleted\r\n",
